connect6: Change in6_pktinfo check

commit.message:
connect6: Change in6_pktinfo check

musl does not define in6_pktinfo which causes a redefinition error.

musl checks against _BSD_SOURCE or _GNU_SOURCE. The latter implies the former.

connect6: Change in6_pktinfo check

musl does not define in6_pktinfo which causes a redefinition error.

musl checks against _BSD_SOURCE or _GNU_SOURCE. The latter implies the former.
